Just click the date of the
meeting and then click New

027ee3e9-222f-4a5e-b606-8a2c78ded561-1
00:01:16.072 --> 00:01:16.480
Meeting.

3ac356a7-1721-42aa-9eb6-cd1adbf08b5a-0
